dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Fox News
dmca.body:
February 15, 2007

VIA FACSIMILE: 650.963.3255

Google, Inc.
Attn: Google Legal Support, DMCA Complaints
1600 Amphitheatre Parkway
Mountain View, CA 94043

RE: DMCA COPYRIGHT INFRINGEMENT NOTIFICATION

Dear Sir or Madam:

It has been brought to the attention of Fox News Network, LLC ("Fox News")
that, as of today's date, the website www.ecotraveler.com ("Website"),
a Blogger blog, includes a reprint the foxnews.com article
